Так же это Chicken Run (NTSC-U) (Eng) (Echelon)

Game.....: Chicken Run (C)
Origin...: USA - NTSC
Released.: November 17th, 2000
Ripped.......: Nothing

Behind the barbed wire fence of Tweedy Farm, Ginger is a chicken with a mission. Fearing for the lives of her friends, she is determined to escape to freedom before it is too late. To do this she enlists the help of Rocky, the smooth talking, flying Rooster...or is he?

Guide a rescue attempt to get all of the chickens to safety before they end up as pies. To do this you will have to sneak around the farm collecting objects necessary for the escape. Be careful not to disturb the dogs and avoid being caught by Mr. and Mrs. Tweedy at all costs in this humorous, 3D action game.

Game Features:
- Based on the Aardman animated film Chicken Run.
- Original film character voices.
- Involving gameplay featuring action, adventure and puzzle solving.
- Control various characters including Ginger, Rocky, and the crafty cockney rodents.
- A large environment to explore involving stealth gameplay, object collection and puzzle solving.